The paper discusses a software solution for assisting users with minimal technical knowledge in traversing through data by following associations. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses object recognition process and data visualization techniques, which are relevant to databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
